'''荷兰路浸信会教堂'''（Holland Road Baptist Church）是[[英格兰|英格兰]]南部城市[[布赖顿-霍夫|布赖顿-霍夫]]的一部分--[[霍夫|霍夫]]的一座[[浸信会|浸信会]]教堂，也是当地南北干道荷兰路上的一处地标。这是该市现存10座浸信会教堂之一，1991年被英国遗产委员会列为登录建筑<ref name="IoE365548">{{cite web|title=Detailed Record: Baptist Chapel and attached schoolroom including forecourt wall, Holland Road (east side), Hove, Brighton and Hove, East Sussex|url=http://www.imagesofengland.org.uk/Details/Default.aspx?id=365548&mode=quick|accessdate=2009-05-03|publisher=[[English_Heritage|English Heritage]]|year=2007|work=[[Images_of_England|Images of England]] website|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023073310/http://www.imagesofengland.org.uk/Details/Default.aspx?id=365548&mode=quick|archive-date=2012-10-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

1887年，一群在西马路体育馆聚会的浸信会教徒筹得资金，在荷兰路兴建自己的永久教堂<ref name="IoE365603">{{cite web|title=Detailed Record: Methodist Church, Portland Road (north side), Hove, Brighton and Hove, East Sussex|url=http://www.imagesofengland.org.uk/Details/Default.aspx?id=365603&mode=quick|accessdate=2009-04-30|publisher=[[English_Heritage|English Heritage]]|year=2007|work=[[Images_of_England|Images of England]] website|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023081041/http://www.imagesofengland.org.uk/Details/Default.aspx?id=365603&mode=quick|archive-date=2012-10-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，当年7月29日举行第一次礼拜。设计者为约翰·威尔斯，哥特复兴风格<ref name="Elleray35">{{Harvnb|Elleray|2004|p=35.}}</ref>。

